1.0.1.name: wordpress/social-links
1.0.1.description:
Social Links is a sidebar widget that displays icon links to your profile pages on other social networking sites.

Supported Networks:

  • Amazon Wishlist
  • Blogs
  • BlogMarks
  • Dapx
  • Delicious
  • Digg
  • Facebook
  • Flickr
  • FriendFeed
  • Jeqq
  • Last FM
  • Linked In
  • My Space
  • Picasa Web Albums
  • Plurk
  • Pownce
  • Sixent
  • Stumble Upon
  • Technorati
  • Twitter
  • YouTube
  • Xing
